title: United Kingdom Imports of Tin & Related Articles
description: Imports of Tin & Related Articles in the United Kingdom decreased to 9.40 GBP Million in September from 12.68 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Tin & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 7 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 20.25 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 2.03 GBP Million in February of 2002. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Tin & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
